Искам да добавя notifications и weekly summary system към DoYouTry.

Notification requirements:
- daily reminder в избран час
- optional second reminder вечерта, ако няма check-in
- hard mode reminders
- push notification support
- notification preferences per user

Примери за messages:
- Did you try today?
- Still time to try.
- No one is coming to save your streak.
- Silence is also an answer.

